    "## Geometric Progressions"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "First term = A\n",
    "\n",
    "Second term = B\n",
    "\n",
    "ratio (r) = B/A\n",
    "\n",
    "nth term = A*r^(n-1)\n",
    "\n",
    "sum of first n terms = A*(1-r^n) / (1-r)"
   ]
  }
